1. Product Background
In the era of globalisation, the importance of the English language is increasing day by day. Nowadays, everyone has to learn English as a mandatory subject. However, this requirement often limits their abilities. There are people who are studying English more and more, but their skills are difficult to develop because they only learn through theoretical knowledge. Their practice and exercises do not target their weaknesses. There are scattered test papers available online, but even if they find a place to gather them, they often lack detailed explanations. With this English training platform, you will find all the test papers you need to enhance your English proficiency, along with highly detailed explanations.
